{"tid":2372153,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"學棍一早預言今屆選舉有舞弊，但去到如今卻反口","createTime":"2021-01-19T11:59:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-19T12:46:42.000Z","uid":261647,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0e0e0c7aa74a93965d8b7c3d880d92efd1e13b2c","tid":2372153,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T11:59:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/henryporterbabel/posts/3601606469935200\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhenryporterbabel%2Fposts%2F3601606469935200&d=CthjHxCXz%2Bl0vOF3eBkmegexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=15c3a7f1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/henryporterbabel/posts/3601606469935200</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZsrTf2r.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZsrTf2r.png&h=e87c06c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n作者：無神論者的巴別塔<br />\n<br />\n【左膠學棍一早預言今屆選舉有舞弊，但去到如今卻反口】<br />\n<br />\n之前「民主教父」Larry Diamond仲響本書度多番提及對選舉舞弊嘅質疑，尤其係電子投票系統嘅不信任，但咁係因為輸果個係希拉莉，贏果個係特朗普<br />\n<br />\n幾年過後佢講嘅選舉舞弊問題真係應驗，呢段文字基本上就係對今次選舉嘅預言<br />\n<br />\n但Larry Diamond今日卻已掉轉槍頭批評所有選舉舞弊質疑都係「假消息」、「陰謀論」，點解？因為自己支持個敗登贏咗丫嘛，個選舉咪即刻變得公平咗囉！<br />\n<br />\n左膠學棍就係咁撚雙重標準"},{"pid":"c6ea3f8166ca8fa385696103a0d4e6dbcff5b40d","tid":2372153,"uid":25797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T12:02:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/HA2DWMHgLnc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FHA2DWMHgLnc&d=CthjHxCXz%2Bl0vOF3eBkmegexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=c1cdc48b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/HA2DWMHgLnc</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1086074b509e17a24599eeee2370a76fe0bb68e4","tid":2372153,"uid":338262,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T12:32:14.000Z","msg":"劉正點睇自己"},{"pid":"5c56225bef4ac93d8dc6d5c55ad8e606dc87a5fd","tid":2372153,"uid":79562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"